Step-by-step for RegCM model users:

I. Pre-processing: (under RegCM/PreProc directory) 

Step I.0: run datalinker.x (after you prepare all the datasets ready) in 
          RegCM/PreProc/DATA/

Step I.1: prepare the terrain and landuse data of your domain (and your
          sub-BATS domain) in RegCM/PreProc/Terrain

Step I.2: prepare the ICBC files of your domain in
          RegCM/PreProc/ICBC 

II. Running the model

Create a RegCM/Run directory, and ... ...

III. Post-processing
